sources.title: The G-String Murders / Lady of Burlesque 1943 | Gypsy Rose Lee, Barbara Stanwyck | Colorized Movie
sources.description:
Mirth! Murder! Melody! Mystery! and Girls! Girls! Girls!
A burlesque dancer finds herself at the center of a murder mystery backstages, and she must unveil the killer's identity before the final curtain falls!

Original title: Lady of Burlesque (1943) AKA: The G-String Murders

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/I-e9dPnFL34

Director: William A. Wellman
Writer: Gypsy Rose Lee, James Gunn 
Stars: Barbara Stanwyck, Michael O'Shea, J. Edward Bromberg 
Genre: Comedy, Mystery, Romance, Burlesque, Musical, Performing Arts

This film is available with additional French & Spanish dubbed audio. Go to video settings ⚙️  to change your audio / subtitle language options.
